; Refuse to install under a toolchain that doesn't match package.json "engines"
; (Node >= 22, npm >= 11). npm 10 silently prunes cross-platform optional deps
; (e.g. @emnapi/*, @rolldown/binding-*) from package-lock.json, which breaks
; `npm ci` on other platforms / CI. Failing loudly here beats a corrupted lockfile.
; See docs/SELF_HOSTING.md ("Updating dependencies") and .nvmrc (Node 24 → npm 11).
engine-strict=true
